OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,FProperty developers in Guernsey are
OL,7,Fproposing a tariff scheme which could
OL,8,Fhelp the States build 'affordable
OL,9,Fhomes'.
OL,11,FThey say a tax could be introduced on
OL,12,Feach accommodation unit they build,
OL,13,Fwhich would help fund social housing.
OL,15,FIt comes after politicians voted to
OL,16,Fscrap Policy GP11 for five years in
OL,17,F2024, a rule which had ensured that
OL,18,Fpart of larger private developments
OL,19,Fhad to be designated for 'affordable
OL,20,Fhomes'.
