OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,FThe original Policy GP11 was first
OL,7,Fintroduced in 2016 to support the
OL,8,FIsland Development Plan and "address
OL,9,Fthe challenge that appropriate housing
OL,10,Fis available to meet all of the island
OL,11,Fcommunity's housing needs".
OL,13,FIt meant any new developments with 20
OL,14,For more dwellings had to provide 26%
OL,15,Fto 30% of the land to the Guernsey
OL,16,FHousing Association, which would then
OL,17,Fallocate it for affordable housing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
