OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,FSpeaking at the time, Deputy Lyndon
OL,7,FTrott said: "States Members have
OL,8,Flistened to the business leaders in
OL,9,Four construction sector, we've
OL,10,Frecognised their concerns about GP11,
OL,11,Fand we've acted to remove that barrier
OL,12,Fbecause getting more houses built is a
OL,13,Ftop priority.
OL,15,F"There are significant sites with the
OL,16,Fpotential for a lot of housing, and
OL,17,Fwith planning permission in place, but
OL,18,Fwe've been told time and again that
OL,19,Fdevelopers can't justify proceeding
OL,20,Fwith them because GP11 puts too big a
OL,21,Fcost onto the projects.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
