OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,F"That cost is gone. Let's get our
OL,7,Fbuilding sector building again, so we
OL,8,Fcan meet the high demand for housing
OL,9,Fand alleviate some of the pressures
OL,10,Four community has faced for too long."
OL,12,FInstead, developers are currently
OL,13,Fcampaigning for a tariff-based system,
OL,14,Fwhere they pay money to the States for
OL,15,Feach unit they build.
OL,17,FITV News understands this could be
OL,18,Fbetween #5,000 and #12,000, depending
OL,19,Fon the size of the accommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
