OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,FThis contribution will then go towards
OL,7,Fsocial housing and enhancing
OL,8,Fbiodiversity.
OL,10,FTom Whitmore, Chair of Guernsey's
OL,11,FBuilding Trades Employers Association,
OL,12,Fexplains: "We support the principle of
OL,13,Fthat contribution coming in, in the
OL,14,Fform of a tariff.
