OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1768993308
OL,3,CCould a tax on new homes fund more
OL,4,C'affordable housing' in Guernsey?
OL,6,F"The reason why we support that as a
OL,7,Fprinciple is that it just provides
OL,8,Fcertainty, you know exactly where you
OL,9,Fstand when you're talking about that
OL,10,Fkind of development site, when you're
OL,11,Frunning the cost planning, and
OL,12,Fultimately looking at land area."
OL,14,FHe adds: "There is a pressing need now
OL,15,Ffor these properties; we need some
OL,16,Fsmall sites that are allocated and can
OL,17,Fbe delivered relatively quickly,
OL,18,Fwithin the next five years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
